DLW-SPUN · the full weave of Aristotle

who   : 'The master of those who know.'
what  : The philosopher all the others defer to, in Limbo's castle.
where : Circle I — Limbo.
why   : Reason perfected — but reason alone cannot reach Heaven.
when  : The same twilight.
how   : Honored above all his peers, and forever one step short.

class : Circle I · Limbo · the virtuous, without grace
